\">[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clickonce](../../../../includes/tla2sharptla-clickonce-md.md)]</ph> automatically handles the mechanics of downloading and starting the application.","pos":[4544,4755],"source":" When the user clicks the link to the .xbap file, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clickonce](../../../../includes/tla2sharptla-clickonce-md.md)] automatically handles the mechanics of downloading and starting the application."},{"content":"The following example code shows an HTML page that contains a hyperlink that points to an XBAP.","pos":[4756,4851]},{"content":"You can also host an XBAP in the frame of a Web page.","pos":[5013,5066]},{"content":"Create a Web page with one or more frames.","pos":[5067,5109]},{"content":"Set the source property of a frame to the deployment manifest file.","pos":[5110,5177]},{"content":"If you want to use the built-in mechanism to communicate between the hosting Web page and the XBAP, you must host the application in a frame.","pos":[5178,5319]},{"content":"The following example code shows an HTML page with two frames, the source for the second frame is set to an XBAP.","pos":[5320,5433]},{"pos":[5642,5663],"content":"Clearing Cached XBAPs","linkify":"Clearing Cached XBAPs","nodes":[{"content":"Clearing Cached XBAPs","pos":[0,21]}]},{"content":"In some situations after rebuilding and starting your XBAP, you may find that an earlier version of the XBAP is opened.","pos":[5667,5786]},{"content":"For example, this behavior may occur when your XBAP assembly version number is static and you start the XBAP from the command line.","pos":[5787,5918]},{"content":"In this case, because the version number between the cached version (the version that was previously started) and the new version remains the same, the new version of the XBAP is not downloaded.","pos":[5919,6113]},{"content":"Instead, the cached version is loaded.","pos":[6114,6152]},{"content":"In these situations, you can remove the cached version by using the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Mage<ept id=